# Mobile App: hex-mob-cleanslate

## Development Environment
- **Framework**: Expo SDK v53
- **Runtime**: React Native 0.79.5 / React 19
- **Package Manager**: bun v1.2.19 (exclusive)
- **Platform Focus**: Android-first development

## Universal Aliases
Instead of ugly relative imports:
```typescript
// ❌ Don't do this
import { PhotoItem } from '../../../../../packages/shared/types/PhotoItem';

// ✅ Do this
import { PhotoItem } from '@shared/types/PhotoItem';
```

## Development Scripts
- `bun run type-check:mobile`: TypeScript validation (mobile-only)
- `bunx expo start --android --localhost --port 8082`: Start Metro server

## TypeScript Configuration
- **Composite project**: References packages/shared for clean type resolution
- **React Native types only**: DOM libs excluded to prevent conflicts
- **Source file references**: No build dependencies, direct type checking